.TH UTILITYKIT 1 "July 2026" "UtilityKit v5.10.6" "UtilityKit Tools"
.SH NAME
utility-yaml_toolkit \- Lint, validate, convert between YAML and JSON, extract values by dot-notation
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B utility yaml_toolkit
[\fIoptions\fP]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Lint, validate, convert between YAML and JSON, extract values by dot-notation
.SH BACKENDS (TRIED IN ORDER)
.PP
.IP \(em 4
\fByq\fP (Go version) — full-featured, recommended
.IP \(em 4
\fBpython3 + PyYAML\fP — pip install pyyaml
.PP
.SH USAGE
.PP
.EX
yaml lint config.yaml
yaml tojson config.yaml
yaml toyml data.json
yaml get config.yaml database.host
yaml keys config.yaml
yaml pretty config.yaml
yaml merge base.yaml overlay.yaml
.EE
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
Flag   |   Meaning   |   Default
\fC--indent N\fP   |   Indentation spaces   |   2
\fC--json\fP   |   Machine-readable output   |   off
\fC--no-color\fP   |   Disable ANSI   |   off
.PP
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.PP
Subcommand   |   Description
\fClint\fP   |   Validate YAML syntax
\fCtojson\fP   |   Convert YAML to JSON
\fCtoyml\fP   |   Convert JSON to YAML
\fCget FILE KEY\fP   |   Extract value by dot-notation
\fCmerge BASE OVERLAY\fP   |   Deep-merge overlay into base
\fCkeys\fP   |   List top-level keys
\fCpretty\fP   |   Pretty-print formatted YAML
.PP
.SH EXIT CODES
.PP
Code   |   Meaning
\fC0\fP   |   Success
\fC1\fP   |   Validation failure or missing key
\fC2\fP   |   No backend available / argument error
